<HEADLINE>
FT  31 MAR 93 / London Stock Exchange: New Highs and Lows for 1992/93
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
NEW HIGHS (79).
AMERICANS (2) Cont'l. Bank, Lowe's, BANKS (1) Allied Irish, BREWERS (1)
